## ğŸ› ï¸ Development

```bash
# Clone repository
git clone <repo-url>
cd quant-pack

# Install with development dependencies
pip install -e .[full,dev]

# Run tests
pytest

# Format code
black src/
ruff check src/ --fix

# Type checking
mypy src/mysingle_quant/
```

